    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Pat</strong> the pork steaks dry with kitchen towel</p>\r\n<p><strong>Trim</strong> off the excess fat (optional)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Rub</strong> them with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(2 tbsp)</span> vegetable oil and coat them evenly in the dried oregano</p>\r\n<p><strong>Season</strong>&nbsp;both sides generously with salt</p>",
      "order": 5,
