      "instruction": "<p><strong>Heat</strong> a wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong> hot, add the pork steaks and cook for 2-3 min on each side, until browned on the outside and cooked through</p>",
