      "instruction": "<p><strong>Transfer</strong> the cooked pork steaks to a plate and cover with a clean tea towel to rest&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Leave</strong>&nbsp;them to rest for 5 min</p>\r\n<p>Tip: Covering with a teatowel keeps the meat warm without steaming it</p>",
